snippet.textDisplay: Allahu Akbar....logo ko Kya ho gaya hai...Allah ke upar nath hi acchi thi....ye music ke sath...guitar, aur duniya bhar ke Haram ke sath Allah na naam Lena...it's totally Haram....aur kahi na kahi tauheen hai Allah pak...logo ko ye samajhna chahiye ki Allah ke zikr ka Kya tareeqa hoga...aur agar tameez nahi hai to sunnate dekhe hmare nabi ki...hm unko bhula baithe.....aap logo isko pasand kaise kr skte hai...just q ki isko sunne ko accha lag rha hai.....Yar hr kaano ko acchi lagne wali cheez sacchi aur acchi nahi hoti....just koi Allah ka naam leta hai to wo bht acchi bat hai...pr is tarah se saaf taur pe tauheen hai...logo ki munafiqat zor mar ke bol rhi hai....Jo aisi bate pasand a rhi hai...hm ye q bhool jate hai...ye bht hi umda kaul ki Quran aur Haram music Dil me 1 sath nahi utar skte....Allah u Akbar...Allah bachaye hmare Muslim bhaiyo ko in fitno se...aur lanat bhejta hu aise logo pe jo ye sb faila rhe hai...Allah inko hidayat de ya inko sabak de.....allahu akbar
